u(x,y)
v(x,y)
M(x,y)dx + N(x,y)dy
u/v
u(x,y) = cv(x,y)
c
y= px + f(p)
x
dp/dx=0
p=c
u
(u M)_y = (uN)_x
u_x = \frac{u (M_y - N_x) + u_y M }{N}
v_x = \frac{v (M_y - N_x) + v_y M }{N}
(u/v)_x = \frac{u_x v - u v_x}{v^2} = \frac{(u_y v - u v_y) M}{N v^2} = \frac{M}{N} (u/v)_y
u/v = c
(u/v)_x \ dx + (u/v)_y \ dy = 0
M \ dx + N \ dy = 0
